v1.07 Added Zones tables, including subnet detection, an unlimited number of zones can now be added with an unlimited number of subnets per zone.
         this completes the missing capabilities from the v1.06 release.
      Added a new demo flow, with very simple UI.

v1.06 Added upstream dns server port capability, this now enables the user to cascade the updnserver nodes to create a zoned system.
      Added some changes to the info pane to reflect the stats capability of the DB.

